                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9029" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0263</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1868 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方甄选的难题：董宇辉的“留”与“去”—“超级员工”的公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The dilemma for EAST BUY: &quot;to fire Dong&quot; or &quot;to keep Dong&quot;?—Corporate governance of &quot;super employees&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于培友，李震，宋翔宇，宁文红</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方甄选（北京）科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方甄选；董宇辉；小作文风波；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">East Buy Holding Limited, Dong Yuhui, Essay storm, Corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年12月6日，东方甄选小编在其官方账号上发布了一则有关东方甄选吉林行的预热视频，并置顶了“宣传文案出自谁手”的解答评论，称经典小作文多数由文案团队创作，并非全部出自主播之手。此事一出，东方甄选受到严重影响，流量下滑，股价暴跌。本案例以“小作文风波”为主线，分别描述了风波前后东方甄选的公司治理模式、对待“超级员工”董宇辉的区别。对董宇辉对于东方甄选的影响以及风波前后东方甄选的公司治理模式做了详细阐述，最后讲述了与辉同行的傲人业绩以及探讨了这种利益分配机制的稳定性。通过本案例引导读者思考“超级员工”的公司治理模式，对类似直播类的超级员工的公司治理提供启发与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On December 6, 2023, the East Buy Holding Limited published a warm-up video about the Eastern Selection of Jilin on its official account, and placed a comment on the answer of &quot;Who wrote the propaganda copy?&quot;, saying that most of the classic essays were created by the copywriting team, not all from the hands of the anchor. Once this happened, Eastern Selection was seriously affected, the flow declined, and the stock price plummeted. This case takes the &quot;small composition storm&quot; as the main line, and describes the difference between the corporate governance model and the treatment of &quot;super employee&quot; Dong Yuhui before and after the storm. This paper expounds the influence of Dong Yuhui on Dongfang Selection and the corporate governance model of Dongfang Selection before and after the incident, and finally describes the proud performance of his peers and discusses the stability of this profit distribution mechanism. This case guides readers to think about the corporate governance model of &quot;super employees&quot; and provides inspiration and reference for the corporate governance of super employees similar to live broadcasting.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《财务管理》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不同环境下的公司治理模式变化；网红直播类公司的公司治理模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
